stateDiagram-v2
    [Education_ClassroomService] --> Initialized: __init__(Education_StudentDB)

    Initialized --> Seeded: set_seed(Education_LMS_Portal)
    
    Seeded --> Running: run(Education_ContentCDN)
    Initialized --> Running: run(Education_LMS_Portal)
    
    Running --> Computing: execution complete
    Running --> Error: exception raised
    
    Computing --> Completed: stats computed
    
    Error --> Initialized: create new instance
    
    Completed --> Running: run(Education_StudentDB) again
    Completed --> [Education_ClassroomService]: return SimulationResult
